graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>React + Fastify]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>cluster]
    Dashboard -->|resource mgmt| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>cluster]
    Dashboard -->|metrics| Thanos[Thanos Querier<br/>cluster]
    Dashboard -->|image metadata| ImageAPI[ImageStream API<br/>cluster]
    Dashboard -->|certificates| CertService[OpenShift Certificate Service<br/>cluster]
    Dashboard -.->|optional| Prometheus[Prometheus/Thanos<br/>cluster]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - CRD Interactions
    Dashboard -->|manages| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>kubeflow.org/notebooks]
    Dashboard -->|model serving| KServe[KServe<br/>serving.kserve.io]
    Dashboard -->|alt serving| ModelMesh[ModelMesh<br/>serving.kserve.io]
    Dashboard -->|versioning| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>modelregistry.opendatahub.io]
    Dashboard -->|pipelines| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
    Dashboard -->|distributed training| DistributedWorkloads[Distributed Workloads]
    Dashboard -->|NVIDIA models| NIMServing[NIM Serving<br/>nim.opendatahub.io]

    %% Platform Configuration Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|reads config| ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js >= 20.0.0]

    %% Integration Points (reverse dependencies)
    ODHDashboardUI[ODH Dashboard UI] -.->|uses| Dashboard
    CLI[kubectl/oc CLI] -.->|creates CRDs for| Dashboard

